                     <decoNote type="none">Otherwise none.</decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <bindingDesc>
                     <binding notAfter="1500" notBefore="1400">
                        <p>Medieval. Bound in half brown leather over wood boards, sewn on three double/slit bands. Flyleaves and former pastedowns using 12th-, 13th-, and 14th-cent. MS. waste. Vestiges of a single clasp. Red fore-edge tabs. Spine with 19th-cent. gilt leather label ‘40’.</p>
                     </binding>
                  </bindingDesc>
